{"tid":867543,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇消防電師父係度？","createTime":"2018-10-18T18:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T18:15:39.000Z","uid":201932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"320f2add8564b583a7346d43af8dc4c9c92b833d","tid":867543,"uid":201932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:03:31.000Z","msg":"想問一下如果 做左一年電燈 <br />\n轉做消防電會唔會好吃力？ <br />\n同埋入大公司定細公司會學得多？<br />\n<br />\n除左拉線做喉 做燈 鐘 閃燈出路燈 同panel之外 <br />\n仲有冇其他野學？ 依加係細公司做緊 得幾個人<br />\n同埋佢地對比之前我做電燈跟既師父 手工真係有差別 而且唔熟panel ....唉 唔想行佢地後路 <br />\n各位師兄有冇人好心點下我 到底點走條路會比較好d<br />\n感恩"},{"pid":"52395fc4dc0610fee40e312480378f8e97793cbb","tid":867543,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:14:43.000Z","msg":"做乜改過個名又開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/19/021441_d2dc489adf760133bd6bf5d75f6f3104.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F021441_d2dc489adf760133bd6bf5d75f6f3104.jpg&h=7404fa0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57217ddd3468bd51565acb58d0e9702ef3065431","tid":867543,"uid":201932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52395fc4dc0610fee40e312480378f8e97793cbb","tid":867543,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:14:43.000Z","msg":"做乜改過個名又開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/19/021441_d2dc489adf760133bd6bf5d75f6f3104.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F021441_d2dc489adf760133bd6bf5d75f6f3104.jpg&h=7404fa0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  哈 呢個名好似貼切d"}]}